#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introducció"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:6
msgid "Welcome to Blender, the free and open source 3D creation suite."
msgstr ""
"Benvingut a Blender, el software de creació de 3D lliure i de codi obert."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:8
msgid ""
"Blender can be used to create 3D visualizations such as still images, video, "
"and real-time interactive video games."
msgstr ""
"Blender és pot utilizar per crear visualizations en 3 dimensions com són "
"imatges, video, i jocs interactius a temps real."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:10
msgid ""
"Blender is well suited to individuals and small studios who benefit from its "
"unified pipeline and responsive development process."
msgstr ""
"Blender s'adapta a persones i petits estudis que es benficien del seu fluxe "
"i el seu process de desarrollo adaptatiu"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:13
msgid ""
"Blender is a cross-platform application, running on Linux, macOS, and MS-"
"Windows systems. Blender also has a relatively small memory and drive "
"requirements compared to other 3D creation suites. Its interface uses OpenGL "
"to provide a consistent experience across all supported hardware and "
"platforms."
msgstr ""
"Blender es una aplicació multiplataforma, que funciona en sistemes Linux, "
"masOS, i MS-Windows. Blender també requreix d'una quantitat de memoria "
"física petita en comparació en altres entorns de creació de 3D. La seva "
"interfície utilitza OpenGL per a proporcionar una experiència consistent a "
"través de totes les plataformes i maquinàris soportats."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:19
msgid "Blender 2.5 with a Big Buck Bunny scene open."
msgstr "Blender 2.5 amb una escena de Big Buck Bunny oberta."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:23
msgid "Who uses Blender?"
msgstr "Qui utilitza Blender?"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:25
msgid ""
"Blender has a wide variety of tools making it suitable for almost any sort "
"of media production. People and studios around the world use it for hobby "
"projects, commercials, feature films, games and other interactive "
"applications like kiosks, games and scientific research."
msgstr ""
"Blender te una ampli ventall d'eines que fan que s'adapti a quasi qualsevol "
"tipus de mitja de producción. Gent i estudis arreu del món l'utilitzen per "
"projectes personals, comercials, pelicules, jocs i altres tipus "
"d'aplicacions com son terminals interactius i investigació científica."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:29
msgid ""
"Check out the `User Stories page <https://www.blender.org/features/user-"
"stories/>`__ on the Blender website for more examples."
msgstr ""
"Dóna una ullada a la  `Pàgina d'històries Personals <https://www.blender.org/"
"features/user-stories/>`__ (en angles) a la web de Blender per a mes "
"exemples."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:34
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "Característiques Clau"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:36
msgid ""
"Blender is a fully integrated 3D content creation suite, offering a broad "
"range of essential tools, including :doc:`Modeling </modeling/"
"introduction>`, :doc:`Rendering </render/introduction>`, :doc:`Animation </"
"animation/introduction>`, :doc:`Video Editing </editors/vse/index>`, :doc:"
"`VFX </editors/movie_clip_editor/index>`, :doc:`Compositing </compositing/"
"introduction>`, :doc:`Texturing </editors/uv_image/uv/overview>`, :doc:"
"`Rigging </rigging/introduction>`, many types of :doc:`Simulations </physics/"
"introduction>`, and :doc:`Game Creation </game_engine/introduction>`."
msgstr ""
"Blender es un  complet entorn de creació 3D, offerint un ampli ventall "
"d'eines, incloent :doc:`Modelat </modeling/introduction>`, :doc:`Renderitzat "
"</render/introduction>`, :doc:`Animació </animation/introduction>`, :doc:"
"`Edició de Video </editors/vse/index>`, :doc:`VFX </editors/"
"movie_clip_editor/index>`, :doc:`Composició </compositing/introduction>`, :"
"doc:`Texturitzat </editors/uv_image/uv/overview>`, :doc:`Rigging </rigging/"
"introduction>`, molts tipus de :doc:`Simulacions </physics/introduction>`, "
"i :doc:`Creació de Jocs</game_engine/introduction>`."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:47
msgid ""
"Cross platform, with an OpenGL GUI that is uniform on all major platforms "
"(and customizable with Python scripts)."
msgstr ""
"Multiplataforma, amb una Interfície d'Usuari OpenGL que es uniforme en totes "
"les principals plataformes (i personalitzable mitjançant Python)"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:48
msgid ""
"High-quality 3D architecture enabling fast and efficient creation work-flow."
msgstr ""
"Arquitectura 3D d'alta qualitat que permet un ràpid i eficient fluxe de "
"treball."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:49
msgid ""
"Excellent community support from `forums <http://blenderartists.org/forum/"
">`__ and :ref:`IRC <irc-channels>`."
msgstr ""
"Excel·lent suport de la comunitat  a través de `forums <http://"
"blenderartists.org/forum/>`__ (anglès) i :ref:`IRC <irc-channels>`."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:50
msgid "Small executable size, optionally portable."
msgstr "Binari de petit tamany, opcionalment portable."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:52
msgid ""
"You can download the latest version of Blender `here <https://www.blender."
"org/download/>`__."
msgstr ""
"Et pots descarregar la última versió de Blender des d'`aquí <https://www."
"blender.org/download/>`__."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:56
msgid "A rendered image being post-processed."
msgstr "Una imatge renderitzada que està sent post-processada."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:58
msgid ""
"Blender makes it possible to perform a wide range of tasks, and it may seem "
"daunting when first trying to grasp the basics. However, with a bit of "
"motivation and the right learning material, it is possible to familiarize "
"yourself with Blender after a few hours of practice."
msgstr ""
"Blender fa possible realitzar una gran quantitat de tasques, i pot semblar "
"desalentador al principi, intentat comprendre els conceptes bàsics. No "
"obstant, amb una mica de motivació i el material d'aprenentatge adecuat, es "
"posible familiarizar-se amb el blender despres d'algunes hores de pràctica."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:62
msgid ""
"This manual is a good start though it serves more as a reference. There are "
"also many online video tutorials from specialized websites, and several "
"books and training DVDs available in the `Blender Store <https://store."
"blender.org/>`__ and on the `Blender Cloud <https://cloud.blender.org/>`__."
msgstr ""
"Aquest manual es un bon inici, tot i que serveix més com una font de "
"referencies. Existeixen també molts video tutorials en línea de llocs web "
"especialitzats, i molts llibres i DVDs de formació disponibles a la `Botiga "
"de blender <https://store.blender.org/>`__ (angles) i al  `Blender Cloud "
"<https://cloud.blender.org/>`__."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:67
msgid ""
"Despite everything Blender can do, it remains a tool. Great artists do not "
"create masterpieces by pressing buttons or manipulating brushes, but by "
"learning and practicing subjects such as human anatomy, composition, "
"lighting, animation principles, etc."
msgstr ""
"Malgrat tot el que és pot fer amb Blender, aquest segueix sent una eina. Els "
"grans artistes no creen obres Mestres apretant botons o manipulant pincells, "
"sinò aprentent i practicant temes com son l'anatomia humana, la composició, "
"la il·luminació, els principis d'animació, etc.."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:71
msgid ""
"3D creation software such as Blender have the added technical complexity and "
"jargon associated with the underlying technologies. Terms like UV maps, "
"materials, shaders, meshes, and \"subsurf\" are the mediums of the digital "
"artist, and understanding them, even broadly, will help you to use Blender "
"to its best."
msgstr ""
"Els entorns de creació 3D com Blender han afegit una complexitat técnica i "
"un argot assossiat a les tecnolgies subjacents. Ternes com mapes UV, "
"materials, shaders, malles, i \"subsurf\" son els mitjans dels artististes "
"digitals, i entendre'ls, fins i tot en general, us ajudarà a treure el màxim "
"profit de Blender."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:76
msgid ""
"So keep reading this manual, learn the great tool that Blender is, keep your "
"mind open to other artistic and technological areas and you too can become a "
"great artist."
msgstr ""
"Per tant, segeix llegint aquest manual, aprèn la gran eina que es Blender, "
"tingues la ment oberta altres arees artístiques i tecnològiques, i tu també "
"pots convertir-te en un gran artista."
